't want people getting multiple copies of the game for cheap. Yet, the developer told them to allow it anyway - that immediately earned my respect. On top of that, these guys areactuallyplaying their own game (shoutout to Thunderfist), and they actually communicate with their players.I love the concept, I'm happy with how they've executed it, and I'm more than pleased with how the developers have presented themselves and treated their fanbase. Honestly if I knew they were gonna' be that cool about things, I probably would have asked to pay full price anyway. As far as I'm concerned, this is already easily worth $15.Keeping my fingers crossed for the futue of Unfortunate Spacemen!- Crunchy Soap™"
